    <td><p class="section_font22"><strong>Call for Papers!</strong></p>
    <p class="bodytext">The journal Machine Vision and Applications (MVA) is pleased to announce a new <a href="https://www.springer.com/journal/138/updates/20145502" target="new">Special Issue on Human Pose Estimation and Its Applications</a>. Dr. <a href="https://tangw.people.uic.edu/">Wei Tang</a>, Dr. <a href="http://web.cs.ucla.edu/~zhou.ren/" target="new">Zhou Ren</a> and Dr. <a href="https://jingdongwang2017.github.io/" target="new">Jingdong Wang</a> are serving as guest editors for this issue. The submission deadline is <u>April 1, 2023</u>. Papers will be reviewed immediately after submission and will be published on an ongoing basis. You are very welcome to contribute your papers! Please visit <a href="https://www.springer.com/journal/138/updates/20145502" target="new">this page</a> for more information and contact the guest editors for any questions.</p></td>
